    <text x="54" y="60" fill="#f8fafc" font-size="30" font-weight="750">Describe the outcome. Inspect the system it builds.</text>
    <text x="54" y="92" fill="#94a3b8" font-size="16">Natural language, Shortcut-style blocks, and source text are three views of the same manifest.</text>

